track_notes:
This is the ascent from Bistriška planina as described on https://www.hribi.net/izlet/bistriska_planina_sentanski_vrh/3/930/1607

Takes around 1 hour 35 minutes. 

Check also a very nice video from S57S/P for more details.
A steeper path from the end of road to S5/KA-029. Šentanski vrh. High hiking boots are recommended.
